  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508780/extras/e0a4a3df6c2fac8dd9f4b031d92e3c6a.poster.avif?t=1771043393\" aria-label=\"Dr. Plague Game Scene\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508780/extras/e0a4a3df6c2fac8dd9f4b031d92e3c6a.webm?t=1771043393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508780/extras/e0a4a3df6c2fac8dd9f4b031d92e3c6a.mp4?t=1771043393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world ravaged by plague, a lone plague doctor embarks on a journey to stop both the disease and a sinister order of knights controlling it. Dr. Plague is a stealth-adventure game that combines puzzle-solving, platforming, and ambient soundtracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through 4 chapters each with a distinct location, ambience & soundtracks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hide and use innovative stealth mechanics to bypass guards, plagues and obstacles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel the mystery of the stalking crows</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rich atmosphere and intense moments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tightly crafted, atmospheric adventure lasting over 2 hours</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508780/extras/f4931befa70d1955c22da02d14380054.poster.avif?t=1771043393\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508780/extras/f4931befa70d1955c22da02d14380054.webm?t=1771043393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508780/extras/f4931befa70d1955c22da02d14380054.mp4?t=1771043393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will You Succeed?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You are not a fighter but you are the only hope. Good luck!</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508780/extras/e0a4a3df6c2fac8dd9f4b031d92e3c6a.poster.avif?t=1771043393\" aria-label=\"Dr. Plague Game Scene\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508780/extras/e0a4a3df6c2fac8dd9f4b031d92e3c6a.webm?t=1771043393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508780/extras/e0a4a3df6c2fac8dd9f4b031d92e3c6a.mp4?t=1771043393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world ravaged by plague, a lone plague doctor embarks on a journey to stop both the disease and a sinister order of knights controlling it. Dr. Plague is a stealth-adventure game that combines puzzle-solving, platforming, and ambient soundtracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through 4 chapters each with a distinct location, ambience & soundtracks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hide and use innovative stealth mechanics to bypass guards, plagues and obstacles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel the mystery of the stalking crows</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rich atmosphere and intense moments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tightly crafted, atmospheric adventure lasting over 2 hours</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508780/extras/f4931befa70d1955c22da02d14380054.poster.avif?t=1771043393\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508780/extras/f4931befa70d1955c22da02d14380054.webm?t=1771043393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508780/extras/f4931befa70d1955c22da02d14380054.mp4?t=1771043393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will You Succeed?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You are not a fighter but you are the only hope. Good luck!</i></p>",
